Matehett, J., dissenting.

Opinion filed July 6, 1934.Elmer W. Arch, for appellants; Elmer W. Arch and Charles H. Borden, of counsel. Jacobson, Merrick, Nierman & Silbert, for appellees; Lewis F. Jacobson, Sidney C. Nierman, David Silbert and Arthur Altschul, of counsel. Mr. Justice MeSurely
